  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1603858">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1603858/" class="title-link">刚开始看</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1603858"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Spartacus/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Spartacus/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-01-01"
      class="main-meta">2009-01-01 09:24:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1603858_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看了前面两章，感觉非常好，没看出大问题，至少阅读起来还顺畅。  但是，将“有限域（finite field）”翻译成“有限场”令我颇为嘀咕了好一阵，对未来的阅读充满了怀疑。翻译者是学理科出身的吗？是不是还有些专有名词翻译不准确？希望看过的，发现问题的都来说说。  国内买不...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1603858/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1603858_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1603858_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
